title: Please Never Fall In Love Again
lyrics: could've been one lonely night just like all the others but you lit up my life this is what it's like to be lovers you and me need never be lonely again spin with me endlessly or at least until the end please never fall in love again Oh, please never fall in love again and if some other guy catches your eye please just text me your goodbye you know i don't look pretty when i cry and i don't want that to be baby but if you could please maybe please never fall in love again Oh, please never fall in love again please.
